Photo by Science Of The Universe 🚀 on July 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'IGI ScienceOfTheUniverse When I was a little kid, was really scared of the dark. But then I came to understand, dark just means the absence of photons in the visible wavelength- 400 to 700 nanometers. Then thought, well, it's really silly to be afraid of a lack of photons.
